I’m thinking about how to summarize duration. If I’m using meta only, it seems I don’t need new CSS, but there’s a requirement for a narrow page and a long title without overflow. The existing item title uses `min-width` with `ellipsis` for the first span. If there are two buttons, maybe I need to adjust the title. Adding CSS for `item-title` to allow `flex-wrap` could help. But including duration in the meta leads me to consider how it might break if the title is too long. I should inspect the RecordCard to see what the body type accepts. It seems like it should be a string and not a ReactNode to avoid issues.
